    "provenance": "GET biome REQUIRED global key; EPA optional (US only); efg + un_elu.* + epa_l3/l4 tagged \"[INFERRED — verify]\" when from a spatial lookup. Coordinates approximate by design (CoordConfidence legend).",
    "us_site": "classify via EPA L1/L3/L4 (convenience) -> confirm/upgrade via IUCN GET biome (coastal -> use MT/MFT transitional realms, not the terrestrial EPA class) -> attach USACE {supplement, hgm, hook} (the regulatory gate) + the archetype money_path (funding); sample ELU per point."
